data.description: Completely remodeled 2 story home, beautifully landscaped, in prime location near dining and shopping.  Brand new everything, down to the insulation and sheet rock.  New stainless steel appliances, cabinets, granite counter tops, kitchen island, sinks, toilets, shower, and tubs.  Large master with 2 walk-in closets, separate tub and shower.  Huge screened in lanai.  Custom diagonal tile throughout most of the house, hardwood in the family room and loft, and carpet in the bedrooms.  Indoor laundry room. New lights and fans throughout.  Freshly painted inside and out.  A MUST SEE.  Call for your appointment today!
